info:
  license:
    name: MIT
  title: Openfaas Swagger
  version: 1.0.0
openapi: 3.0.0
paths:
  /serverdecommission:
    post:
      requestBody:
        content:
          text/plain:
            schema:
              properties:
                serverName:
                  type: string
                userMSID:
                  type: string
              type: object
        description: user to add to the system
      responses:
        5XX:
          description: Internal API Error.
        "200":
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                example: Server Decommission successful
                type: string
          description: Decommission message
        "404":
          description: Invalid server.
        "417":
          description: Invalid Data.
      summary: Funcion to decommission a server
  /serverlesspoc:
    post:
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: object
      responses:
        "200":
          description: success
  /testgradle:
    post:
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              properties:
                serverName:
                  type: string
              type: object
        description: user to add to the system
      responses:

          description: Internal API Error.
        "200":
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                example: Server Decommission successful
                type: string
          description: Decommission message
        "404":

        "417":
          description: Invalid Data.

  /testing:
    post:
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:

      responses:
        "200":
          description: success
  /testopenfaasfunction:

          application/json:

      responses:
        "200":
          description: success
